## 8. `DefaultCdcResultMapper`

Maps each `ResultSet` row into a `CdcEvent`. Reads standard LogMiner metadata columns directly. Delegates business data columns (`SQL_REDO`, `SQL_UNDO`) to `CdcRowMapper`:

```java
public class DefaultCdcResultMapper implements CdcResultMapper {

    private final CdcRowMapper rowMapper;

    @Override
    public List<CdcEvent> map(ResultSet rs) throws SQLException {
        List<CdcEvent> events = new ArrayList<>();
        while (rs.next()) {
            OperationType operation = OperationType.valueOf(rs.getString("OPERATION"));
            Map<String, Object> data = rowMapper.mapRow(
                rs.getString("SQL_REDO"),
                rs.getString("SQL_UNDO"),
                operation
            );
            events.add(CdcEvent.builder()
                .scn(rs.getLong("SCN"))
                .schema(rs.getString("SEG_OWNER"))
                .tableName(rs.getString("SEG_NAME"))
                .operation(operation)
                .timestamp(rs.getTimestamp("TIMESTAMP").toInstant())
                .data(data)
                .build());
        }
        return events;
    }
}
```

