### 11.3 `CdcAutoConfiguration`

```java
@AutoConfiguration
@EnableConfigurationProperties(CdcProperties.class)
@ConditionalOnBean(annotation = EnableCdc.class)
public class CdcAutoConfiguration {

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcConnectionProvider cdcConnectionProvider(DataSource dataSource) {
        return new DataSourceCdcConnectionProvider(dataSource);
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CurrentScnProvider currentScnProvider() {
        return new DefaultCurrentScnProvider();
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcResultMapper cdcResultMapper(CdcRowMapper rowMapper) {
        return new DefaultCdcResultMapper(rowMapper);
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CheckpointStrategy checkpointStrategy(DataSource dataSource,
                                                   CdcProperties properties) {
        return new JdbcCheckpointStrategy(dataSource,
            properties.getCheckpoint().getTableName());
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcEventHandler cdcEventHandler(DataSource dataSource,
                                            CdcProperties properties) {
        return new JdbcCdcEventHandler(dataSource,
            properties.getPersistence().getTableName());
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcErrorHandler cdcErrorHandler() {
        return new DefaultCdcErrorHandler();
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcLifecycleListener cdcLifecycleListener() {
        return new CdcLifecycleListener() {};  // no-op
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcClient cdcClient(CdcConnectionProvider connectionProvider,
                                CdcQueryProvider queryProvider,
                                CdcResultMapper resultMapper) {
        return new DefaultCdcClient(connectionProvider, queryProvider, resultMapper);
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcEngine cdcEngine(CdcClient client,
                                CurrentScnProvider currentScnProvider,
                                CheckpointStrategy checkpointStrategy,
                                CdcEventHandler eventHandler,
                                CdcErrorHandler errorHandler,
                                CdcLifecycleListener lifecycleListener,
                                List<CdcEventFilter> filters,
                                CdcProperties properties) {
        return new CdcEngine(client, currentScnProvider, checkpointStrategy,
            eventHandler, errorHandler, lifecycleListener,
            filters, toPollingConfig(properties));
    }

    // Missing mandatory beans — fail fast
    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcQueryProvider missingQueryProvider() {
        throw new CdcConfigurationException(
            "No CdcQueryProvider bean found. Provide a CdcQueryProvider bean to use the CDC starter.");
    }

    @Bean
    @ConditionalOnMissingBean
    public CdcRowMapper missingRowMapper() {
        throw new CdcConfigurationException(
            "No CdcRowMapper bean found. Provide a CdcRowMapper bean to use the CDC starter.");
    }
}
```

### 11.4 `CdcSchedulingConfiguration`

```java
@Configuration
@ConditionalOnBean(CdcEngine.class)
public class CdcSchedulingConfiguration {

    private final CdcEngine engine;

    @Scheduled(fixedDelayString = "${platform.cdc.polling.interval:5000}")
    public void poll() {
        engine.tick();
    }
}
```

Uses `fixedDelay` (not `fixedRate`) — next tick starts only after the previous tick (including all catchup iterations) has fully completed.

