## 16. Error Behaviour Reference

| Failure point | Default behaviour | Checkpoint advances? | Engine stops? |
|---|---|---|---|
| `poll()` throws | log, skip tick | No | No |
| `eventHandler.handle()` throws | log, throw fatal | No | Yes |
| `checkpointStrategy.saveScn()` throws | log, throw fatal | No | Yes |
| `getCurrentScn()` throws | propagates as `CdcPollingException` | No | Depends on caller |

